Title: Wonder Woman: Bloodlines
Writer: William Moulton Marston (Wonder Woman created by), Mairghread Scott (screenplay)
Actors: Marie Avgeropoulos, Kimberly Brooks, Ray Chase, Rosario Dawson
Plot: Wonder Woman tries to help a troubled young girl, Vanessa, who has fallen in with a deadly organization known as Villainy Inc. headed by Dr. Cyber.
